          <title>Reproducción sexual</title>
          <description><![CDATA[<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; float: left; width: 561.25px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">
<p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Algunos protistas se reproducen sexualmente a trav&eacute;s de&nbsp;<strong>isogametos</strong>, que al unirse forman&nbsp;un&nbsp;<strong>cigoto</strong>.</span></span></p>

<p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Protistas&nbsp;multicelulares&nbsp;como las&nbsp;<strong>algas</strong>, realizan <strong>alternancia de generaciones</strong>, es decir:</span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Una generaci&oacute;n lleva a cabo la fase&nbsp;<strong>asexual</strong></span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">La siguiente generaci&oacute;n realiza reproducci&oacute;n&nbsp;<strong>sexual</strong>.</span></span></li>
</ul>
</div>
]]></description>
